headline.main: Atkinson Is Aboard Five Victors, Including Gold Box, at Aqueduct; ATKINSON WINNER ON 5 AT AQUEDUCT

results.snippet: Last Friday was Ted Atkinsons's thirty - ninth birthday. Backers of the great jockey's mounts had no reason to bake him any cakes. He was beaten on three successive favorites.
